{"tid":674130,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有玩扑驚嘅面孔","createTime":"2018-05-22T12:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T22:43:44.000Z","uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de4330958242194cf849edbd9cedd57f1723b442","tid":674130,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打都鍾意玩扑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 我最近收咗隻以前同friend喺某扑驚鋪玩過嘅驚 叫terra mystica(中文好似叫神秘大陸) <br />\n<br />\n收嘅途中發現原來佢出咗新version 叫terra mystica Gaia project 有冇巴打玩過/睇過人玩 覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我買terra mystica嗰陣 條友sell我買Twilight Struggle 有冇巴打可以講下覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知開喺咩台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開喺活動台又好似真係搵人出嚟玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea45912bc543768764014493fec3af19d95c650","tid":674130,"uid":179571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4ed8441c909af925b7d19f6f7d6ff7637fe0d76","tid":674130,"uid":12421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ea45912bc543768764014493fec3af19d95c650","tid":674130,"uid":179571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"我冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f758f8584f8d4adf0ddff419593a8c97bcffa29","tid":674130,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c538098ee5e55a5160af89ecf8108133e1c8e1f1","tid":674130,"uid":4512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:50:15.